Business Model Overview
Our platform is a web‑based marketplace that connects individuals seeking
companionship for social activities with people offering their time. 
Users can browse profiles, book companions for events, trips, dinners,
or everyday outings, and pay securely through the app. We operate on a 
commission‑based model: each booking generates revenue through service 
fees charged to both the client and the companion. 
Additional income streams include premium profile boosts, subscription
tiers for enhanced visibility, and in‑app safety verification services. 
By combining transparent pricing, user reviews, and a streamlined booking experience,
we create a trusted environment where people can easily find the right 
person to accompany them in any social situation.
